short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Brings you updates on new cases of COVID-19 (Coronavirus)

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
COVID-19 Reporter brings you latest reports/updates on COVID-19 (CoronaVirus) cases from reliable sources.

It provides you with detailed information on, new and existing cases, recovered, and deaths; cases/million, deaths/million, recovery and death percentage etc.

Inbuilt interactive chart, enables you to analyse the data.

Provides you with a worldwide summary with quick search option.
